org.openbel.framework.compiler
Interface DefaultPhaseFour

All Known Implementing Classes:
PhaseFourImpl
public interface DefaultPhaseFour

BEL compiler phase four interface.

Phase four compilation consists of:

  1. Stage 1 -- Create KAMstore
    Create the KAMstore schema using the database connection.

Author:
Anthony Bargnesi <abargnesi@selventa.com>

stage4LoadKAM

void stage4LoadKAM(DBConnection dbConnection,
                   ProtoNetwork p2pn,
                   String kamSchemaName)
                   throws DatabaseError,
                          CreateKAMFailure
Executes stage four loading of KAM using a DBConnection database connection against a KAMstore schema.

Parameters:
dbConnection - DBConnection, the database connection
p2pn - ProtoNetwork, the phase II proto network output
Throws:
CreateKAMFailure - Thrown if the KAM schema to be loaded does not exist
DatabaseError - Thrown if a database error occurred while loading the KAM.
